creator: My.com B.V.
descriptionHtml:
MY.GAMES App is a companion app that will make your interactions with the MY.GAMES Store platform and its services easier and more secure. Protect your account with two-factor authentication and be the first to know about the events that take place in your favorite games and on the MY.GAMES Store platform.

TWO-FACTOR AUTHENTICATION
The main function of the application is two-factor authentication. It will ensure that no one can use your MY.GAMES account data without your knowledge, so your accounts in Warface, Conqueror's Blade, Skyforge, and other games will be safe. Confirming a request through the mobile application is extremely simple: just tap "Confirm" or "Reject".

NOTIFICATIONS
Receive notifications from your favorite MY.GAMES games and services. Get informed straightaway about unique promotions, new friends and gifts!
descriptionShort: Protect your account with two-factor authentication
